HEADWORD: Calculary
<hw>Cal"cu*la*ry</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A congeries of little stony
knots found in the pulp of the pear and other fruits.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

